1 Sec. 3. Section 77-2603.01, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska, is
2 amended to read:
3 77-2603.01 The state may, as part of enter into an agreement with an
4 Indian tribe entered into pursuant to section 77-2602.06, contemplate
5 which contemplates the use of a tribal stamp for sales of cigarettes on
6 an Indian tribe's Indian country in lieu of the cigarette stamp required
7 under section 77-2603.
8 Sec. 4. Original sections 77-2602.05, 77-2602.06, and 77-2603.01,
9 Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska, are repealed.
